oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Nashville man trout fishing in Tellico River
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of Owen Hughes of Nashville trout fishing in the Tellico River in East Tennessee. Owen Hughes is standing in the river with river bank and trees behind him. Hughes is dressed in pants and shirt with hat. He has a fishing pole, net and bag along with four trout already caught.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: RG 82: Tennessee Department of Conservation Photograph Collection, 1937-1976
